snippet.title: TheFlamingShark
snippet.description:
A reactor of anime and cartoons who once got up to 200,000 subscribers before unfortunate complications arose. Currently my channel is using a rotation of five series, in which Slots 1, 3, and 5 are for Anime, and Slots 2 and 4 are for Western series. Also, I apparently do Let's Plays now.

Slot 1: Monogatari
Slot 2: The Dragon Prince
Slot 3: My Hero Academia
Slot 4: Amphibia
Slot 5: JoJo's Bizarre Adventure: Diamond is Unbreakable

Danganronpa 2: Goodbye Despair Let's Play on Fridays

Klaus Reaction on Christmas Day

Spirited Away & The Iron Giant Reuploads: December 30th or if I need an upload before that for some reason.

I also react to one movie a month based on a Patreon Poll, so go join my Patreon if you want to be a part of those polls. Occasionally we have series polls there as well to determine shows I will do in the future.
